---
import sideImg from '@/assets/images/b6de27df4c69.png';
---

<section class="section section--tint hair-why">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="hair-why__head">
      <h2 class="hair-why__heading">
        Why Choose Menon Medispa for Your Hair Restoration Needs?
      </h2>
      <p class="hair-why__intro">
        Our comprehensive approach integrates advanced scalp care with medical-grade procedures to deliver truly transformative results. We create customized treatment plans that address both immediate concerns and long-term hair wellness goals.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hair-why__layout">

      <div class="hair-why__media-col">
        <img
          src={sideImg.src}
          alt="Menon Medispa hair restoration treatment in Millburn NJ"
          class="hair-why__side-img"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="315"
          height="313"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="hair-why__text-col">

        <div class="hair-why__block">
          <h3 class="hair-why__block-heading">Our Integrated Treatment Philosophy</h3>
          <p class="hair-why__block-body">
            At Menon Medispa, we understand that optimal hair restoration often requires a multi-faceted approach. Our specialists are trained in both scalp health and advanced procedures like HydraFacial Keravive and PRP hair therapy, allowing us to create personalized solutions that enhance your natural hair growth potential.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hair-why__block">
          <h3 class="hair-why__block-heading">What to Expect</h3>
          <p class="hair-why__block-body">
            Your experience begins with a thorough consultation to understand your hair concerns and goals. Whether you&rsquo;re receiving a HydraFacial Keravive treatment or PRP hair restoration therapy, you&rsquo;ll enjoy attentive care in our relaxing, clinical environment. We use only premium products and advanced techniques to ensure safe, effective results.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hair-why .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hair-why__head {
    max-width: 820px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .hair-why__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .hair-why__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hair-why__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Left column: sticky on desktop */
  .hair-why__media-col {
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hair-why__side-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.12);
  }

  /* Right column: accent-ruled text blocks */
  .hair-why__text-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hair-why__block {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-cta);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .hair-why__block-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-subheading);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .hair-why__block-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hair-why__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hair-why__media-col {
      position: static;
      max-width: 315px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
